<plot>Exit Signs is a short film about a man emotionally paralyzed in the prime of his life. Without goals or ambitions, he is drifting across the country, sleeping in his car, cleaning up in public restrooms, and encountering random people. He leaves cryptic phone messages for his family, promising to return home, but he home he returns to is not the one he left.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?185393</url></doc>
